    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jeepney Stories</strong> is a heartwarming, slice-of-life, funny and chill visual novel about family, chances, getting old and living in the third world set in the bustling city of Manila, Philippines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203470/extras/264e523950b61efbcf40a0a735cb2b50.poster.avif?t=1743041734\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203470/extras/264e523950b61efbcf40a0a735cb2b50.webm?t=1743041734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203470/extras/264e523950b61efbcf40a0a735cb2b50.mp4?t=1743041734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Day 1 to Day 7 Adventures</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join &quot;Mang Paldo&quot; in his daily adventures and conversations with people from different walks of life, culture and status. <strong>Jeepney Stories</strong> has different endings depending on how you play the game and interact with your passengers' fare. Give the incorrect change or &quot;more&quot; money and you alter the fate of the different characters in the game and ultimately, the game's final ending.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203470/extras/6ef6e6f7c75c58a2802147ac66b9be10.poster.avif?t=1743041734\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203470/extras/6ef6e6f7c75c58a2802147ac66b9be10.webm?t=1743041734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203470/extras/6ef6e6f7c75c58a2802147ac66b9be10.mp4?t=1743041734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy and listen to different stories of passengers who ride with Mang Paldo in his Jeepney.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Branching storylines for different characters depend on how you interact with the passenger's fare (a little bit of math required in giving change LOL).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn cartoon graphics. 95% of the art was created using an iPad and Procreate (I'm proud of it)!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Catchy, cozy and chill soundtracks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An unforgettable experience that we hope you can learn something from. 😊</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203470/extras/c2d084d0e5b543897fdce95f5da1f677.poster.avif?t=1743041734\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203470/extras/c2d084d0e5b543897fdce95f5da1f677.webm?t=1743041734\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203470/extras/c2d084d0e5b543897fdce95f5da1f677.mp4?t=1743041734\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Happy playing! 😊😊😊</p>",
